parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the camshaft position sensor can cause the engine to stall or shut down, leading to a loss of power and potentially causing accidents. It can also cause the check engine light to illuminate, leading to further engine damage if not addressed.
symptoms: The check engine light illuminates
the engine stalls or shuts down
smoke comes from under the hood
the vehicle is unable to restart
the engine sensor light stays on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The inability to get recall repairs done in a timely manner can lead to further engine damage, accidents, and financial losses for vehicle owners.
symptoms: Dealerships are not in operation
dealerships refuse to honor the recall
no authorized service centers are available in the area
parts are not available
dealerships have long waiting lists.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The inability to find a dealer to perform air bag recall repairs can lead to a safety risk, as the air bags may not deploy properly in the event of an accident, potentially causing injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: None
as this issue is related to the recall process rather than a specific symptom or malfunction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the air bags to deploy in the event of an accident can lead to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Air bags did not deploy in an accident
SRS light appeared on the dashboard
air bags deployed late or only after the vehicle had rolled several times.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A defective front safety belt can cause discomfort, distraction, or even injury in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The belt would not extend and retract properly
resulting in a very tight and uncomfortable fit.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake hose can cause a loss of brake fluid, leading to a loss of braking power, which can increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: None reported
as the complaints primarily concern the inability to have the recall performed due to a lack of available dealers.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brakes can cause a loss of control, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The brakes do not hold when applied
the brakes are spongy or soft
the brakes fail to stop the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The inability to have recalls performed or issues addressed by dealers can lead to a delay in necessary repairs, potentially increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: Dealers are not available to perform recalls
dealers refuse to honor recalls
dealers are unresponsive to consumer concerns.
